&lt;p&gt;The article is interesting even for those who don’t know what a &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Media_center" class="liwikipedia"&gt;Media Center&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Htpc" class="liwikipedia"&gt;Home Theater PC&lt;/a&gt; are.&lt;/p&gt;
